        {
          "type": "heading-two",
          "commit": "7c0fcad0b2ab3a029cb86ee842672d7ad4558ed5",
          "id": "c9ybnK39F4",
          "fixed": true,
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "初始化 Express 博客"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "explain",
          "fixed": true,
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "children": [
                {
                  "text": "很多公司都有搭建自己的技术博客的需求，那么灵活度高的搭建技术博客的技术中 Express 可以排的上名头了，所以我们公司选用了 Express 来搭建我们的技术博客。"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "children": [
                {
                  "text": "首先我们安装 "
                },
                {
                  "text": "Node.js",
                  "link": true,
                  "url": "https://nodejs.org"
                },
                {
                  "text": " ，然后我们通过运行如下命令检测命令是否安装成功："
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "code-block",
              "lang": "bash",
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "code-line",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "text": "node -v # v12.16.1"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "code-line",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "text": "npm -v # 6.13.4"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "children": [
                {
                  "text": "上面的命令运行成功之后，我们就成功初始化了环境，接着我们允许如下命令来初始化这个博客："
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "code-block",
              "lang": "bash",
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "code-line",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "text": "npx express-generator our-tuture"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "children": [
                {
                  "text": "运行上面的命令之后，Express 的脚手架会自动创建一个简单的 Express 项目，然后运行如下命令开启一下创建好的 Express 项目："
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "code-block",
              "lang": "bash",
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "code-line",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "text": "cd our-tuture && npm install"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "code-line",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "text": "npm start"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "children": [
                {
                  "text": "接着打开浏览器 "
                },
                {
                  "text": "http://localhost:3000/",
                  "link": true,
                  "url": "http://localhost:3000/"
                },
                {
                  "text": "，应该可以看到如下界面："
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "image",
              "url": ".tuture/assets/image.png",
              "children": [
                {
                  "text": ""
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "children": [
                {
                  "text": ""
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "children": [
                {
                  "text": "恭喜你，成功搭建起公司博客的原型，接下来我们来讲解一下具体的代码。"
                }
              ]
            }
